---
const base = import.meta.env.BASE_URL;
---
<section class="story" id="about">
  <div class="story-pattern" aria-hidden="true"></div>
  <div class="container story-inner">

    <div class="story-text">
      <span class="section-label">The Taqueria</span>
      <h2 class="section-title story-heading">Made for Late Nights<br/>and Big Cravings</h2>
      <p class="story-body">
        There's something about a warm corn tortilla at midnight that just hits different.
        Enrico's Tacos is the kind of place that fills a real need in Dunedin —
        real Mexican street food, open late, right on Patricia Ave.
      </p>
      <p class="story-body">
        Think rich salsa, handmade-style masa, slow-cooked meats, and tacos
        built for sharing. Whether you're stopping in after a long shift or
        just chasing a late-night craving, the food here is the kind that keeps
        you coming back.
      </p>
      <ul class="story-pillars">
        <li>
          <span class="pillar-dot" style="background: var(--salsa)"></span>
          <span>Late-night hours, Mon – Sat until midnight</span>
        </li>
        <li>
          <span class="pillar-dot" style="background: var(--tomatillo)"></span>
          <span>Mexican street-food favorites done right</span>
        </li>
        <li>
          <span class="pillar-dot" style="background: var(--amber)"></span>
          <span>Tacos made for sharing around the table</span>
        </li>
        <li>
          <span class="pillar-dot" style="background: var(--clay)"></span>
          <span>A casual, neighborhood taqueria feel</span>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="story-img-wrap">
      <img
        src={`${base}images/chillies.jpg`}
        alt="A vibrant pile of fresh red, orange, and green chili peppers"
        class="story-img"
        loading="lazy"
      />
      <div class="story-img-caption">
        <img
          src={`${base}images/al-pastor-tacos.jpg`}
          alt="Al pastor street tacos on a hand-painted Mexican terracotta clay plate"
          class="story-img-inset"
          loading="lazy"
        />
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .story {
    background: var(--charcoal);
    color: var(--crema);
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  /* Subtle papel picado–inspired dot pattern */
  .story-pattern {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background-image: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(255,255,255,0.04) 1px, transparent 1px);
    background-size: 28px 28px;
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  .story-inner {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 4rem;
    align-items: center;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .story .section-label {
    color: var(--amber-light);
  }

  .story-heading {
    color: var(--crema);
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
  }

  .story-body {
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: #c4bdb4;
    line-height: 1.75;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .story-pillars {
    list-style: none;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.65rem;
    margin-top: 1.5rem;
  }

  .story-pillars li {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.75rem;
    font-size: 0.93rem;
    color: #d6cfc0;
  }

  .pillar-dot {
    width: 9px;
    height: 9px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .story-img-wrap {
    position: relative;
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    overflow: visible;
  }

  .story-img {
    width: 100%;
    aspect-ratio: 3 / 4;
    object-fit: cover;
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-lg);
  }

  .story-img-caption {
    position: absolute;
    bottom: -1.5rem;
    left: -1.5rem;
    width: 55%;
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    overflow: hidden;
    box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);
    border: 3px solid var(--charcoal);
  }

  .story-img-inset {
    width: 100%;
    aspect-ratio: 4 / 3;
    object-fit: cover;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .story-inner {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 2.5rem;
    }

    .story-img-wrap {
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    }

    .story-img-caption {
      bottom: -1rem;
      left: -1rem;
    }
  }
</style>
